<plot>Ms. Pullman is a court-appointed arbitrator who must take on the dreaded Helms family lead by bitter patriarch August, his underachieving son Brian and his wily, widowed ex-son-in-law Jonny, an industrial plastics engineer who has created a strange deathbed keepsake to remember his deceased wife Susan. Now the family is at odds over who should own it. A satire loosely inspired by real events.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?317956</url></doc>
